188
00:12:25,264 --> 00:12:28,364
Right Eun Jo?! Seung Jo is a waiter!

189
00:12:28,364 --> 00:12:30,964
I want to see him too

190
00:12:30,964 --> 00:12:35,031
Then shall the three of us have dinner there tomorrow?

191
00:12:35,031 --> 00:12:36,236
Huh?

192
00:12:37,523 --> 00:12:39,131
