276
00:17:53,689 --> 00:17:55,456
What would you like?

277
00:17:55,456 --> 00:17:57,256
Give me anything.

278
00:17:57,256 --> 00:17:58,856
Yes, I understand.

279
00:17:58,856 --> 00:18:02,123
