284
00:18:27,323 --> 00:18:29,189
This big...

285
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:30,789
Is this a duck?

286
00:18:30,789 --> 00:18:33,660
Not a duck... a chicken.

287
00:18:35,702 --> 00:18:37,889
