300
00:20:14,423 --> 00:20:15,798
Customer!

301
00:20:19,023 --> 00:20:21,023
There isn't much time until we close.

302
00:20:21,023 --> 00:20:23,089
Ah... yes.

303
00:20:23,389 --> 00:20:25,023
It's 123,000 won all together.

304
00:20:26,979 --> 00:20:29,180
What's that expensive?

305
00:20:29,823 --> 00:20:32,856
You had a Super Special Set and 7 cups of coffee.

306
00:20:32,856 --> 00:20:34,856
Super... whatever it is... how much is it?

307
00:20:34,856 --> 00:20:36,756
It is 58000 won.

308
00:20:39,489 --> 00:20:40,956
A moment please.

309
00:20:53,189 --> 00:20:54,656
Wait a moment please.

310
00:21:06,089 --> 00:21:07,423
Here.

311
00:21:07,423 --> 00:21:08,656
Yes.

312
00:21:08,656 --> 00:21:10,223
Thank you.

313
00:21:13,689 --> 00:21:18,356
Excuse me. Until what time does Baek Seung Jo work?

314
00:21:22,889 --> 00:21:25,260
Aye, tell me.

315
00:21:25,260 --> 00:21:28,989
