316
00:21:28,989 --> 00:21:30,856
Ah, really?

317
00:21:30,856 --> 00:21:31,856
Thank you.

318
00:21:32,589 --> 00:21:34,089
At 9 pm?

319
00:21:35,089 --> 00:21:37,523
Since it's 8:30 now...

320
00:21:39,189 --> 00:21:41,256
He should be getting off soon.

321
00:21:41,256 --> 00:21:42,223
Good.

322
00:21:42,223 --> 00:21:46,556
Today, I will go see where Seung Jo lives.

323
00:21:47,189 --> 00:21:49,156
Of course, just slightly.

324
00:22:16,723 --> 00:22:17,756
Were you waiting?

325
00:22:17,756 --> 00:22:18,894
I just came out.

326
00:22:19,426 --> 00:22:21,489
Really? It is a relief.

327
00:22:21,489 --> 00:22:23,689
Oh, I am tired.

328
00:22:23,689 --> 00:22:25,889
-Let's hurry
-Okay.

329
00:22:36,571 --> 00:22:39,163
They're just going together because they live in the same area.

330
