It has to be like that.

331
00:23:39,505 --> 00:23:40,882
What is this?

332
00:23:41,071 --> 00:23:43,138
Seung Jo...

333
00:23:43,138 --> 00:23:44,615
With Hae Ra...

334
00:25:17,105 --> 00:25:18,605
Ha Ni! What happened?

335
00:25:18,605 --> 00:25:20,306
Why are you so late?

336
00:25:20,306 --> 00:25:23,938
I was worried. It's past midnight already.

337
00:25:25,771 --> 00:25:27,271
I am sorry.

338
00:25:27,271 --> 00:25:29,794
Was there a club meeting?

339
00:25:31,071 --> 00:25:33,038
Did something happen?

340
00:25:33,038 --> 00:25:35,438
No, everything is alright.

341
00:25:36,998 --> 00:25:40,471
What about a bath? Should I get the water ready for you?

342
00:25:40,471 --> 00:25:43,671
I am just going to sleep today.

343
00:25:44,089 --> 00:25:45,805
Good night.

344
00:25:48,271 --> 00:25:50,238
Okay.

345
00:25:50,238 --> 00:25:51,762
Good night.

346
00:25:57,477 --> 00:25:58,729
Strange.

347
00:26:28,495 --> 00:26:31,029
Seung Jo, who used to be right next door...

348
00:26:31,029 --> 00:26:34,150
now lives with Hae Ra now.

349
00:26:34,150 --> 00:26:37,440
What was all that talk about not hating me?

350
00:26:37,729 --> 00:26:40,034
He doesn't hate me...

351
00:26:40,034 --> 00:26:42,562
but he likes He Ra. Is that it?

352
00:26:51,862 --> 00:26:53,995
Right now, those two...

353
00:27:13,995 --> 00:27:15,569
I'll be back.

354
00:27:15,569 --> 00:27:17,395
Oh my, Ha Ni!

355
00:27:18,445 --> 00:27:20,438
There are dark circles under your eyes!

356
00:27:20,438 --> 00:27:22,695
And your eyes are swollen.

357
00:27:22,695 --> 00:27:24,995
You look a bit sickly.

358
00:27:25,411 --> 00:27:26,829
Really?

359
00:27:26,829 --> 00:27:28,895
I couldn't sleep that well.

360
00:27:28,895 --> 00:27:31,020
Aren't you studying too much?

361
00:27:31,020 --> 00:27:32,929
That could never happen.

362
00:27:33,895 --> 00:27:35,329
Are you okay?

363
00:27:35,329 --> 00:27:37,561
What do you think about taking a day off of school today?

364
00:27:37,561 --> 00:27:38,473
I'm okay.

365
00:27:38,473 --> 00:27:43,129
If you feel worse, ask Seung Jo to bring you home.

366
00:27:43,129 --> 00:27:48,829
If you show that face to our hyung, he'll probably faint.

367
00:27:48,829 --> 00:27:50,695
He probably will.

368
00:27:50,695 --> 00:27:53,295
I better be careful.

369
00:27:53,295 --> 00:27:54,962
Then, I'll be back.

370
00:27:55,862 --> 00:27:57,262
Hey Ha Ni, what about breakfast?

371
00:27:57,262 --> 00:27:59,162
I don't have an appetite.

372
00:27:59,939 --> 00:28:01,157
Then.

373
00:28:08,429 --> 00:28:12,635
What do you think happened to Ha Ni?

374
00:28:12,635 --> 00:28:18,068
It seems like it's not something normal.

375
00:28:18,068 --> 00:28:20,019
What could it be?

376
00:28:21,723 --> 00:28:23,929
Ah, really!

377
00:28:23,929 --> 00:28:25,447
Are you on a diet?

378
00:28:25,447 --> 00:28:28,759
Why aren't you eating these days?!

379
00:28:28,759 --> 00:28:30,888
It's because I don't have an appetite...

380
00:28:30,888 --> 00:28:34,153
What's the matter? It's because of Baek Seung Jo, isn't it?

381
00:28:34,153 --> 00:28:36,607
Tell us, we will listen.

382
00:28:37,304 --> 00:28:38,975
I...

383
00:28:40,810 --> 00:28:42,891
think I'll just give up now.

384
00:28:42,891 --> 00:28:44,037
Aigoo!

385
00:28:44,037 --> 00:28:46,220
I've heard that more than a hundred times before.

386
00:28:46,220 --> 00:28:47,102
Right?

387
00:28:47,102 --> 00:28:48,867
My ears refuse to hear it.

388
00:28:49,726 --> 00:28:52,722
But I really mean it this time...

389
00:28:56,853 --> 00:28:57,907
What?!

390
00:28:57,907 --> 00:28:59,432
Living together?!

391
00:29:00,315 --> 00:29:02,474
Yoon Hae Ra and Beak Seung Jo?!

392
00:29:02,474 --> 00:29:04,285
Didn't you see it wrong or something?

393
00:29:05,144 --> 00:29:07,675
But still,

394
00:29:07,675 --> 00:29:11,414
staying at home together for more than one hour and not going out,

395
00:29:11,414 --> 00:29:14,177
Wouldn't they be in that kind of relationship. . .

396
00:29:19,239 --> 00:29:22,141
Seeing that it became like this,

397
00:29:22,990 --> 00:29:26,298
I must have liked Seung Jo very much.

398
00:29:26,839 --> 00:29:30,129
I could feel it all the way in my bones.

399
00:29:31,597 --> 00:29:35,655
Crushes are really painful...

400
00:29:37,699 --> 00:29:39,015
Ha Ni...

401
00:29:39,015 --> 00:29:41,089
What to do?

402
00:30:05,284 --> 00:30:07,309
Hello everyone.

403
00:30:22,929 --> 00:30:29,967
1, 2, 3.

404
00:30:29,967 --> 00:30:31,383
Back to the starting position!

405
00:30:31,383 --> 00:30:38,303
1, 2, 3.

406
00:30:38,303 --> 00:30:39,742
Back to the starting position!

407
00:30:39,742 --> 00:30:42,831
1, 2, 3.

408
00:30:42,831 --> 00:30:45,013
Hey Oh Ha Ni! Won't you go back to your senses?!

409
00:30:45,013 --> 00:30:45,803
Yes.

410
00:30:45,803 --> 00:30:51,910
1, 2, 3.

411
00:31:34,806 --> 00:31:37,135
Hey! Baek Seung Jo!

412
00:31:41,073 --> 00:31:42,174
Who are you?

413
00:31:42,785 --> 00:31:45,099
"Who... Who are you?"

414
00:31:45,748 --> 00:31:49,743
We've been around each other for so long, and you're saying you don't know who we are?

415
00:31:49,743 --> 00:31:51,439
We are Oh Ha Ni's friends.

416
00:31:52,623 --> 00:31:54,155
You have an IQ of 200

417
00:31:54,155 --> 00:31:55,688
but you can't even remember that?

418
00:31:55,688 --> 00:31:58,731
We weren't in the same class,
but we went to the same high school!

419
00:31:58,731 --> 00:32:01,586
I immediately erase useless data out of my head, you know.

420
00:32:02,073 --> 00:32:04,392
Ah, I remember!

421
00:32:04,392 --> 00:32:07,275
The two who have the same level of brains as Oh Ha Ni,

422
00:32:07,275 --> 00:32:08,784
Jung Joo Ri and...

423
00:32:08,784 --> 00:32:10,595
Go Min Ah, right?

424
00:32:12,058 --> 00:32:13,637
What's the matter?

425
00:32:13,637 --> 00:32:16,590
Ah really, what did Ha Ni like about a guy like you...

426
00:32:16,590 --> 00:32:17,932
You're right.

427
00:32:18,861 --> 00:32:19,697
What did you want to say?

428
00:32:19,697 --> 00:32:21,010
Hey!

429
00:32:21,010 --> 00:32:22,159
Don't you think, you were too much?

430
00:32:22,159 --> 00:32:24,434
It's about Ha Ni, do you know?

431
00:32:24,434 --> 00:32:28,196
In the last 10 days she looks like she's been through hell and back!

432
00:32:28,196 --> 00:32:29,682
As her friend,

433
00:32:29,682 --> 00:32:31,531
I can't just sit and watch her like this!

434
00:32:31,531 --> 00:32:32,947
So what?

435
00:32:32,947 --> 00:32:34,233
What is it you want to say?

436
00:32:34,604 --> 00:32:37,064
Living together!

437
00:32:37,064 --> 00:32:38,991
Living together?

438
00:32:38,991 --> 00:32:43,163
What? You want to stand here and deny it now?

439
00:32:43,163 --> 00:32:46,771
That you are living together with Yoon Hae Ra!

440
00:32:46,771 --> 00:32:51,290
Ha Ni said, she followed you two
and saw everything with her own eyes!

441
00:32:51,290 --> 00:32:53,094
Ha Ni, the poor thing,

442
00:32:53,094 --> 00:32:56,256
Waited for more than one hour on the street!

443
00:32:56,256 --> 00:32:57,685
Although you know about Ha Ni's feelings,

444
00:32:57,685 --> 00:32:59,217
Did you have to leave home like this,

445
00:32:59,217 --> 00:33:01,446
and even live with another woman?

446
00:33:01,446 --> 00:33:03,258
At least clear everything up first!

447
00:33:03,258 --> 00:33:05,099
You're such a coward.

448
00:33:05,099 --> 00:33:06,950
Don't fool around behind her back!

449
00:33:06,950 --> 00:33:08,947
Be a man and tell her the truth!

450
00:33:08,947 --> 00:33:12,337
Fine. All I have to do is tell her the truth?

451
00:33:13,428 --> 00:33:17,631
If you're too honest then it'll be bad for Ha Ni so...

452
00:33:17,631 --> 00:33:22,275
She's a lot more sensitive than what she looks to be...

453
00:33:23,947 --> 00:33:27,476
So what we're saying is to stop tormenting Ha Ni!

454
00:33:27,476 --> 00:33:31,168
We're not telling you to stop liking Yoon Hae Ra.

455
00:33:31,168 --> 00:33:32,817
You understand, right?

456
00:33:32,817 --> 00:33:36,718
Tell her there's no hope and to give up.

457
00:33:36,718 --> 00:33:38,434
Oh Ha Ni...

458
00:33:38,434 --> 00:33:40,649
has been in a one-sided love with you for 4 years.

459
00:33:40,649 --> 00:33:43,660
That's what we wanted to say.

460
00:33:45,588 --> 00:33:48,297
We'll get going now.

461
00:33:48,297 --> 00:33:49,256
Let's go.

462
00:33:59,550 --> 00:34:01,424
Here. You were hungry right?

463
00:34:01,424 --> 00:34:03,351
Wow!

464
00:34:04,187 --> 00:34:05,580
This is abalone.

465
00:34:05,580 --> 00:34:07,198
This is mountain root.

466
00:34:07,198 --> 00:34:08,909
This is duck.

467
00:34:08,909 --> 00:34:12,592
Here Ha Ni eat up, it's a treat from Joon Gu and us.

468
00:34:13,057 --> 00:34:15,156
You have to take care of your body.

469
00:34:15,156 --> 00:34:17,863
And find a new love.

470
00:34:17,863 --> 00:34:19,217
That's right, Ha Ni.

471
00:34:19,217 --> 00:34:21,277
Hey, that's not important.

472
00:34:21,277 --> 00:34:23,181
Is he the only man in this world?

473
00:34:23,181 --> 00:34:26,176
Look around you, there are so many gorgeous man out there...

474
00:34:27,825 --> 00:34:29,729
You're right...

475
00:34:31,772 --> 00:34:34,466
But I have no appetite...

476
00:34:34,466 --> 00:34:36,555
You guys eat up.

477
00:34:36,555 --> 00:34:37,670
Hey, Ha Ni...

478
00:34:37,670 --> 00:34:39,435
You taking it this hard...

479
00:34:39,435 --> 00:34:41,471
Is absolutely killing me.

480
00:34:42,191 --> 00:34:43,754
You should eat a little.

481
00:34:51,168 --> 00:34:55,231
I haven't seen Seung Jo in two weeks already.

482
00:34:55,231 --> 00:34:56,687
Yeah...

483
00:34:56,687 --> 00:34:58,730
Without me trying...

484
00:34:58,730 --> 00:35:03,165
There was no way for us to meet like this.

485
00:35:04,861 --> 00:35:08,011
What are you doing here?

486
00:35:08,011 --> 00:35:10,039
Are you waiting for someone?

487
00:35:12,268 --> 00:35:14,241
Long time no see...

488
00:35:16,633 --> 00:35:19,296
I haven't seen you around lately.

489
00:35:19,296 --> 00:35:22,392
Yeah that's right...

490
00:35:22,392 --> 00:35:24,396
Then I'm going to go first.

491
00:35:24,396 --> 00:35:27,454
Show some compassion.

492
00:35:27,454 --> 00:35:29,822
Can't you sit with me while I wait for someone?

493
00:35:29,822 --> 00:35:34,048
Well...I guess.

494
00:35:36,045 --> 00:35:40,085
Well... how is it? The new house?

495
00:35:40,085 --> 00:35:41,502
Oh...

496
00:35:41,502 --> 00:35:44,683
It's good. The rooms are spacious.

497
00:35:45,463 --> 00:35:47,323
Yeah...

498
00:35:48,175 --> 00:35:51,045
What about meals?

499
00:35:51,045 --> 00:35:52,787
Well,

500
00:35:52,787 --> 00:35:56,084
Sometimes I eat at my part-time job.

501
00:35:56,084 --> 00:35:58,452
Sometimes someone cooks for me.

502
00:35:58,452 --> 00:36:00,867
C-cooks for him?

503
00:36:02,137 --> 00:36:04,327
When you're suddenly living on your own,

504
00:36:04,327 --> 00:36:05,674
it must be quite lonely.

505
00:36:05,674 --> 00:36:07,438
Well, it isn't even like that.

506
00:36:07,438 --> 00:36:09,064
For the most part,

507
00:36:09,064 --> 00:36:12,315
I'm with Yoon Hae Ra quite often.

508
00:36:15,008 --> 00:36:18,259
Ah... yeah...

509
00:36:19,513 --> 00:36:21,788
Teacher!

510
00:36:23,312 --> 00:36:25,857
I'm here!

511
00:36:25,857 --> 00:36:27,215
You're good about being on time.

512
00:36:27,215 --> 00:36:29,915
Coming to Parang University, which is my target...

513
00:36:29,915 --> 00:36:32,841
I'm really starting to think that I need to study really hard.

514
00:36:33,352 --> 00:36:34,543
Omo!

515
00:36:34,543 --> 00:36:36,161
This unnie...

516
00:36:36,161 --> 00:36:38,089
are you maybe Oh Ha Ni unnie?

517
00:36:38,089 --> 00:36:39,552
Ah...

518
00:36:39,552 --> 00:36:41,920
- How do you know me?
- I knew it!

519
00:36:41,920 --> 00:36:44,196
She's exactly the way teacher Hae Ra described.

520
00:36:44,492 --> 00:36:48,236
I can recognize her instantly. I heard a lot about you.

521
00:36:48,236 --> 00:36:49,419
Ah yes...

522
00:36:49,570 --> 00:36:51,770
Huh?! What did you hear about me?

523
00:36:51,770 --> 00:36:58,289
I heard that you were the bottom of the school, but with the help of teacher Baek Seung Jo that you got into the top 50!

524
00:36:58,936 --> 00:37:01,447
I heard that's still a legend!

525
00:37:01,447 --> 00:37:03,736
Ah. Well, yes...

526
00:37:04,270 --> 00:37:05,436
Teacher!

527
00:37:09,436 --> 00:37:10,505
Did you wait long?

528
00:37:10,505 --> 00:37:12,436
No, I just came.

529
00:37:13,570 --> 00:37:18,403
I'm getting English tutoring from Hae Ra teacher and math tutoring from Seung Jo teacher,

530
00:37:18,403 --> 00:37:21,440
because I'm going to take the entrance exam for this school.

531
00:37:21,440 --> 00:37:23,703
Then your teachers...

532
00:37:23,703 --> 00:37:28,436
They come over at least 3 times a week. My mom loves them.

533
00:37:28,436 --> 00:37:30,570
She even cooks them meals all the time.

534
00:37:32,170 --> 00:37:37,470
But, it seems like Hae Ra teacher and Ha Ni unnie are not that close.

